BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Amazing Amphibians\, McCormick's Creek State Park
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260522T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260522T120000
UID:f3cd0fdf78cda84751521096526cdf0a@events.in.gov
DESCRIPTION:(Naturalist Station) Did you know that some salamanders do not
  have a larval stage? Meet Naturalist Jessica at the Nature Center to lear
 n about other amazing amphibian facts and to meet some amphibian friends.
LOCATION:McCormick's Creek State Park\, Nature Center\, 250 McCormick's Cr
 eek Park Road\, Spencer\, IN 47460
URL:on.in.gov/mccormickscreek
X-SOURCE:McCormick's Creek State Park
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Tea with Trees\, McCormick's Creek State Park
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260522T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260522T120000
UID:d0f5a655cbc6f60639f8d488d55139be@events.in.gov
DESCRIPTION:(Naturalist Station) Drop into the Nature Center anytime betwe
 en 10 am-12pm to try some native teas that come from trees. &nbsp\;
LOCATION:McCormick's Creek State Park\, Nature Center\, 250 McCormick's Cr
 eek Park Road\, Spencer\, IN 47460
URL:on.in.gov/mccormickscreek
X-SOURCE:McCormick's Creek State Park
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Critters of the Night\, McCormick's Creek State Park
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260522T210000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260522T223000
UID:70bdf61620b75bf7e835d659433ff03c@events.in.gov
DESCRIPTION:(Night Hike) Critters are flying crawling and climbing all nig
 ht long but most people never see them because of the darkness. Join Natur
 alist Kaitlyn at Deer Run Shelter for a safe and fun way to learn about th
 e nocturnal animals of Indiana. Bring a redlight flashlight or borrow one 
 from us. This hike is 1.2 miles. &nbsp\;
LOCATION:McCormick's Creek State Park\, Deer Run Shelter\, 250 McCormick's
  Creek Park Road\, Spencer\, IN 47460
URL:on.in.gov/mccormickscreek
X-SOURCE:McCormick's Creek State Park
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Weaving Demostration\, McCormick's Creek State Park
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260523T140000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260523T160000
UID:16260147b57504f208447df6259e6b96@events.in.gov
DESCRIPTION:(Weaving Demonstration) Did you know that weaving has existed 
 since 500 B.C. and we still use this skill today! Come see a weaving demon
 stration by DNR Volunteer and Fiber Artist Denise Buckingham. Denise will 
 be creating textiles out of spun wool fibers. You see this demonstration i
 n the Nature Center. &nbsp\;
LOCATION:McCormick's Creek State Park\, Nature Center\, 250 McCormick's Cr
 eek Park Road\, Spencer\, IN 47460
URL:on.in.gov/mccormickscreek
X-SOURCE:McCormick's Creek State Park
END:VEVENT
