BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Salamander Search Party\, McCormick's Creek State Park
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260530T140000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260530T160000
UID:6cbb829e332e763bd235a33519928d6a@events.in.gov
DESCRIPTION:(Naturalist Station) Indiana is home to 5 lungless salamander 
 species\, many of which can be found in Wolf Cave Nature Preserve. Stop by
  our table at Twin Bridges on Trail 5 to meet some wild caught critter and
  attempt to discover them yourself.&nbsp\; &nbsp\;
