SUMMARY:Fossil Naturalist Station\, McCormick's Creek State Park
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260531T150000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260531T160000
UID:43d3d1781cd91680ca3e58602be9c9d1@events.in.gov
DESCRIPTION:(Activity) Did you know the fossils inside of Indiana`s state 
 rock is older than dinosaurs? Stop by our Naturalist Station in the Nature
  Center to do a fun family activity to learn more about limestone and the 
 fossils inside them. &nbsp\;
LOCATION:McCormick's Creek State Park\, Nature Center\, 250 McCormick's Cr
 eek Park Road\, Spencer\, IN 47460
URL:on.in.gov/mccormickscreek
