BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Operation Firewatch
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260731T160000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260731T160000
UID:3a67e3e8e892782d9c55d72a4892ffbe@events.in.gov
DESCRIPTION:Some of you are barely hanging on. Some of you are running on 
 empty. And some ofyou&hellip\; have been one bad day away from tapping out
 . We&rsquo\;re not here to sugarcoat it. We&rsquo\;ve buried too many of o
 ur own. It&rsquo\;s time to stop bleeding alone. Operation Firewatch is no
 t a vacation. It&rsquo\;s where warriors stand guard over each other&rsquo
 \;s lives\, stories\, and futures. July 31\, 2026 at 4pm - August 2\, 2026
  at 10am Scholarships available\, please do not let cost prevent youfrom c
 oming.
LOCATION:McCormick's Creek State Park\, 250 McCormick's Creek Park Road\, 
 Spencer\, IN 47460
URL:https://irreverentwarriors.donordrive.com/firewatch26
X-SOURCE:McCormick's Creek State Park
END:VEVENT
